"sdk.collaboraonline.com/docs/installation/Proxy_settings.html"
msgstr ""
"無法建立插座連線或插座連線意外關閉。反向代理可能設定錯誤，請聯絡管理員。關於"
"代理組態的更多資訊，請參閱 https://sdk.collaboraonline.com/docs/installation/"
"Proxy_settings.html"

